data.description: **Hello, Future Homeowner!** Dive into the vibrant vibes of the Bayshore Arts District with this fabulously unique gem! Freshly revamped, she’s flaunting a spacious, breezy floorplan, a brand-new kitchen, and oh-so-shiny stainless steel appliances. And did we mention the tile flooring throughout? Yep, she's got that too. Sheltered under a brand-new roof, this beauty stretches out on an impressive one-and-a-half lots. That’s a whole lot of space for Bayshore! A huge benefit to this property is that there are NO rental restrictions!   Feeling the urge for a garden stroll? The Naples Botanical Gardens is just a hop, skip, and a jump away! If sailing's more your style, set sail from a public marina merely a mile away. Hungry for a taste of local culture? Delight in the nearby attractions: buzzing Celebration Park, enticing restaurants, fabulous shopping, inspiring art galleries, and so much more. It's also just a short drive to Downtown Naples and beautiful white sandy beaches. Property video available.
